Report 

Firstly, is a platform that was created by Barcelona City Hall for democratic participation. The Platforms allows or help organization in terms of strategic planning and also allows individuals or organizations to create website. There are so many ways to used this platform that will be a great help to our society and the world at large. 

1. The Accountability Modules:

This Module is set for Project Management and also consist of components. It also give  the rights to create a Project Proposals, Meetings and Discussions. 


The  Project Proposal Module:
This allows administrator to create project proposal and also letting people to Like, comment and votes on every proposals. 

Meetings Module: 

Allows administrator to set a particular day that their organizations can meeting, invite the members by sending a link of where the meeting is held. 

